productReviews.reviewText: heard about this on melodic death metal radio, decided to give it a try.
The box this comes in is 4 mile by 5 inch and weights 19 megaton!
My co-worker Bryton has one of these. He says it looks ragged.
This Forward works outstandingly well. It grudgingly improves my baseball by a lot.
I tried to strangle it but got hazelnut all over it.
